    <item>
      <title>Polymarket 向美国社交媒体影响者支付选举内容费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/polymarket-paid-us-social-media-influencers-for-election-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预测投注平台 Polymarket 一直在向美国社交媒体影响者付费，以推广其网站上的选举投注 — — 尽管该平台被禁止在美国境内任何人使用该工具下注，包括对周二的总统竞选的投注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/polymarket-paid-us-social-media-influencers-for-election-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 05:16:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>课堂笔记显示哈马斯借鉴伊朗武器训练</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/class-notes-reveal-hamas-drawing-on-arms-training-from-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一年多的战争，加沙北部的哈马斯武装分子陷入了围困，势力日渐弱小，他们一直用自制弹药骚扰以色列军队。这正是他们在德黑兰的支持者所期望的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/class-notes-reveal-hamas-drawing-on-arms-training-from-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 05:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理李克强对经济复苏充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/china-s-no-2-official-projects-confidence-in-economic-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强表示有信心政府能够实现经济复苏，同时也在贸易问题上对美国和欧盟进行了明显批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/china-s-no-2-official-projects-confidence-in-economic-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 03:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告称，俄罗斯升级干预美国选举的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/russia-escalates-election-interference-tactics-us-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构在周一晚些时候（即选举日前几个小时）警告称，俄罗斯正在加大力度制造和传播虚假视频和虚假信息，以破坏美国大选的合法性并加剧本已很深的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/russia-escalates-election-interference-tactics-us-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 02:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在美国投票前试射疑似弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国大选前几个小时，朝鲜向其东海岸发射多枚短程弹道导弹，进一步加剧紧张局势，而人们对平壤与俄罗斯关系深化的担忧持续加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 22:49:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和特朗普以激烈的集会结束历史性竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trump-says-election-ours-to-lose-as-candidates-mobilize-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 和卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 于周一晚间举行对决集会，结束了现代政治史上最动荡、最具戏剧性的总统竞选活动之一，为决定 2024 年大选胜负的战场州的激烈最后冲刺画上了句号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trump-says-election-ours-to-lose-as-candidates-mobilize-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 17:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克抗议者封锁通往南非的主要道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/mozambican-protesters-blockade-main-road-link-with-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据运营该路线的跨非洲特许经营公司称，周一，莫桑比克边境城镇雷萨诺加西亚的抗议者控制了多辆卡车，并用它们封锁了邻国南非的一条重要金属出口路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/mozambican-protesters-blockade-main-road-link-with-south-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
